{"tid":85317,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾俊華：政府注資強積金　每人六千","createTime":"2017-01-18T08:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T09:24:08.000Z","uid":50329,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b1f459bc13494483a47911ec84bb8a4bd49c408e","tid":85317,"uid":50329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T08:46:13.000Z","msg":"曾俊華：政府注資強積金　每人六千<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.crntt.com/doc/1016/0/8/0/101608033.html?coluid=93&amp;kindid=6811&amp;docid=101608033\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.crntt.com%2Fdoc%2F1016%2F0%2F8%2F0%2F101608033.html%3Fcoluid%3D93%26kindid%3D6811%26docid%3D101608033&d=gVeYQ2KYjX1ddR1HfhwbSqEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=4b9da3c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.crntt.com/doc/1016/0/8/0/101608033.html?coluid=93&amp;kindid=6811&amp;docid=101608033</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2011-02-23 14:03:31&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n　　中評社香港2月23日電／香港財政司長曾俊華今天宣布，向所有擁有強積金的市民，一次過派發6000元，注入他們的強積金戶口。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n　　曾俊華在財政預算案中表示，為增加強積金和職業退休計劃成員的退休儲蓄，建議為所有在今年2月23日已成為強積金計劃或職業退休計劃下，受香港《僱傭條例》涵蓋的成員的人士，向他們的強積金戶口一次過注入6，000元。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n　　他指出，這次的注資建議不設收入上限，希望協助更多市民為退休作好準備。這既不會增加通脹壓力，也是政府現在財政上可負擔的。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n　　他表示，已經為這項措施預留240億元。財經事務及庫務局稍後會公布詳情，積金局會協助執行注資工作。他希望在2011至12年度內，開始向有關的強積金戶口注入款項。"},{"pid":"f1e259d35208ad2f04e54ccad5cc19b6312e255d","tid":85317,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T08:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSEdxvwcQZ9a9rQLr9cKmLJEevxUh7v8YGkdHpxBiaWAV?filename=huOK4V1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhuOK4V1.jpg&h=d3481527&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8e34118a851e51c015faed2c292e4e9c068dfe1","tid":85317,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T08:54:59.000Z","msg":"屌你咩樓主，講撚夠幾年前啲新聞未呀？"},{"pid":"e00d7494addceded093cccfbdce13211effc88ff","tid":85317,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:24:08.000Z","msg":"貼埋啲舊聞嚟把撚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}